value.title: Interpretación de la ecuación
value.description:
La ecuación matemática se puede reescribir como: Eq(-3 * `y(x)` + 5 * DERIVA("y(x)", "x") - 
4 * DERIVA("y(x)", "x", 2) + DERIVA("y(x)", "x", 3) - 
2 * DERIVA("y(x)", "x", 4) + DERIV
value.latex_description: \text{Se reescribe como: } - 3 y{\left(x \right)} + 5 \frac{d}{d x} y{\left(x \right)} - 4 \frac{d^{2}}{d x^{2}} y{\left(x \right)} + \frac{d^{3}}{d x^{3}} y{\left(x \right)} - 2 \frac{d^{4}}{d x^{4}} y{\left(x \right)} + \frac{d^{5}}{d x^{5}} y{\left(x \right)} = 0
